data.title: Celebrate for Natalie Buchanan & Will Warner
data.meta_description: Natalie Buchanan and Will Warner have registered at Bloomingdale's for their wedding on October 13, 2024. Visit MyRegistry.com to shop their Bloomingdale's registry and more.
data.text:
